==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tarantass
<hw>Tar`an*tass"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Russ.
<ets>tarantas'</ets>.]</ety> <def>A low four-wheeled carriage used in
Russia. The carriage box rests on two long, springy poles which run from
the fore to the hind axletree. When snow falls, the wheels are taken
off, and the body is mounted on a sledge.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tarantella</ent>⟦br⟧
